      <h2 style="color: #ff6f61;font-size: 1.5rem;">Kitten Care</h2>
      <p style="margin: 1rem 0;">Kittens under a year old need kitten-specific wet and dry food, access to a clean litter box from an early age, and plenty of toys and scratching posts for play. It’s important to start vaccinations and deworming early, and socialization should begin as soon as possible.</p>
